{
    "version": 4,
    "bundle": "PXHJVHDFQBVR5G25SPWDIDR33YEGUIPS",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "820028002",
    "title": "いつか、『物語』の主役に",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "放課後、トレーニングの参考資料を\r\n探しに訪れた図書室で――",
            "enText": "After school, I went to the library to find \nsome reference material for my training.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "pathId": 3400335588903977602,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……ふふ。",
            "enText": "… Phew.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "pathId": 6679989414657239835,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "いつになく楽しそうに読書している、\r\nゼンノロブロイを見かけた。",
            "enText": "I saw Zenno Rob Roy reading a book, which she \nseemed to enjoy more than ever.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "何を読んでるんだ？",
                    "enText": "What are you reading?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "何を読んでるの？",
                    "enText": "What are you reading?",
                    "nextBlock": 4
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3123908713073106019,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "あ……。\r\nこの本、ですか？",
            "enText": "Oh… This book, is it?",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "pathId": -9177047665886994665,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "『西洋英雄譚集・決定版』――\r\n実は、私の大好きな1冊なんです。",
            "enText": "The definitive collection of Western heroic \ntales - actually, one of my favourite books.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "英雄が好きなんだ？",
                    "enText": "Do you like heroes?",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2785564332729641145,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "はい……えっと。\r\n……興味、ありますか？",
            "enText": "Yes… Um… Are you interested in…?",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ああ",
                    "enText": "Oh.",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "うん",
                    "enText": "Yeah",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2130065749162619706,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "わぁ……嬉しいですっ！\r\n英雄譚って、とっても素敵なんですよ！",
            "enText": "Wow… I'm so happy! Heroic \ntales are so wonderful!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "pathId": -9000005293650148928,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "――誰もが最初から立派だったわけじゃない。\r\n無名だった英雄も、たくさんいます。",
            "enText": "—Not everyone was great from the start. \nThere are many heroes who were unknown.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "pathId": 3167927822538963865,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "でも……そこから、少しずつ強くなって。\r\n数々の試練や苦難を乗り越えて――",
            "enText": "But… from there, we gradually became \nstronger. We've been through a lot of trials \nand tribulations.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "pathId": 4026381870002712105,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "そして最後は……！　みんなの注目を、\r\n一身に浴びるまでの存在になるんです……！",
            "enText": "And finally…! We're going to be the one to \nget all the attention…!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "pathId": 7955658204553482381,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……それで、劇的な物語を読んでいると、\r\n私も――そんなふうになりたいなって。",
            "enText": "… So, when I read dramatic stories, \nI wanted to be like that.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "pathId": -2636503105811139476,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "今は引っ込み思案で、目立たない私でも……。\r\nいつか、英雄みたいな“主役”にって……！！",
            "enText": "At the moment I'm a shy and unobtrusive \nperson. One day, I'll be a hero, a \"star\"…!",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "pathId": 6879108330666836122,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……だから、私は――",
            "enText": "It's… so I—",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "英雄に憧れてるんだな",
                    "enText": "You admire heroes.",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "英雄に憧れてるんだね",
                    "enText": "You admire heroes.",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3280493982462628115,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "――あっ。\r\nす、すみません……！",
            "enText": "—Oh. Sorry, sorry…!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "pathId": 9003799057463884414,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "つい、熱が入って……。\r\n私ばかり喋ってしまいました。",
            "enText": "I was so passionate about… \nI was talking too much.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "pathId": 4428414620908342911,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "それで……えっと。\r\nあなたは、どうして図書室に？",
            "enText": "So… let's see. What brings \nyou to the library?",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "pathId": 1776481391703225692,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ゼンノロブロイに、トレーニングの\r\n参考資料を探しにきたと伝えた。",
            "enText": "I told Zenno Rob Roy that I had come to look \nfor a training reference.",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "pathId": 5725927775411781077,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "なるほど……。\r\nもし、ご迷惑でなければ……ですが。",
            "enText": "I see… If you don't mind, I'm…",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "pathId": 1631690173074590597,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "話を聞いてくださったお礼に、\r\n私にもお手伝いさせてください……！",
            "enText": "Thanks for listening and let me help you…!",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "pathId": -2210162700337891277,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "私、図書委員ですから……ここの蔵書には、\r\nそれなりに詳しいつもりなので……。",
            "enText": "I'm a member of the library committee, \nso … I'm reasonably familiar with \nthe books in the library…",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ありがとう",
                    "enText": "Thank you.",
                    "nextBlock": 21
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 457141731543114242,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "その後、ゼンノロブロイと一緒に\r\n選んだ本をしばらく読み込んだ……。",
            "enText": "Afterwards, I spent some time reading the \nbook I had chosen with Zenno Rob Roy…",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "pathId": -5344648877179302,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "そうだ……最後に、この英雄譚の\r\nエピソードを紹介させてください。",
            "enText": "That's right… Finally, allow me to introduce \nyou to this heroic episode.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "英雄譚も参考になるんだ？",
                    "enText": "Is there a reference to the heroic tale too?",
                    "nextBlock": 23
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7445859105092423334,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "ええ、きっと。\r\nこの英雄はなんと！　ですね――",
            "enText": "Yes, I'm sure. What a hero! Yes…",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "pathId": -6866528469297512248,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "自分と巨大な牛とを縄で繋いで、\r\n引っ張り合って体を鍛えていたんです。",
            "enText": "She used to rope herself and a huge bull and \npull them together to strengthen her body.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "すごい……",
                    "enText": "Amazing…",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8937707419203595140,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "ふふっ、本当に。\r\nたくましさが溢れていますよね。",
            "enText": "Phew, really. That's a lot of toughness.",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "pathId": 6809810757077530899,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "私も、トレーニングの時は\r\nその気概を見習って取り組んでいます。",
            "enText": "I try to emulate that spirit when I train.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "頑張ってるんだな",
                    "enText": "You're doing great.",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "頑張ってるんだね ",
                    "enText": "You're doing great.",
                    "nextBlock": 27
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1599063653552240337,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "……はいっ。",
            "enText": "Go to…",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "pathId": -4299827672548394671,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "たとえ今は……無名だったとしても。\r\n英雄たちのように、いつか必ず――",
            "enText": "Even if they are… unknown now. Like our \nheroes, one day we will…",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "pathId": -6498942362784700126,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ゼンノロブロイ",
            "enName": "Zenno Rob Roy",
            "jpText": "私が“主役”の物語を……。\r\nレースを、見せるつもりですから……！",
            "enText": "I'm the \"star\" of the story… I'm \ngoing to show you the race…!",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "pathId": -9207751477876099189,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そう告げたゼンノロブロイの眼差しには、\r\n強い決意が宿っているように見えた……。",
            "enText": "Zenno Rob Roy's eyes looked determined \nas she said this…",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "pathId": 1489217789389487236,
            "blockIdx": 30
        }
    ]
}